{"TopicId":145675,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"Reflecting on the past: The old Mk1 cockpit","CreatedByName":"HafCoJoe","CreatedById":80363,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-09T19:19:55Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"HafCoJoe","CreatedById":80363,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-09T19:19:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI want to take a moment and appreciate the old sci-fi concept plane cockpit we used to have up until 0.25\u00A0as well as it\u0027s cleaned up version by\u00A0the\u00A0summer intern\u00A0Hugo which we had up until v1.1 when it was revamped by \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/92433-porkjet/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002292433\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/92433-porkjet/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Porkjet\u003C/a\u003E\u00A0for a\u00A0sleek private-jet style\u00A0and happily received\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E. A lot of us can agree that it needed a new face, but there still\u00A0is a certain demeanor to it\u0027s original design.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cimg alt=\u0022pcpjE1C.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/pcpjE1C.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022UX6tVeM.png?1\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/UX6tVeM.png?1\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSometimes it\u0027s nice to appreciate what we\u0027ve come from.\u00A0If you guys like this sort of thing I might do more of these on occasion. Ta ta for now.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-08-09T20:20:31Z\u0022 title=\u002208/09/2016 08:20  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 9, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Avera9eJoe\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"regex","CreatedById":70807,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-09T19:33:11Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNever really liked it, myself. \u00A0Seemed like a Kerbal\u0027s head would never fit inside of it\u00A0or they\u0027d be all hunched over due to ~enormous forehead~ and unable to raise their eyes up enough to actually see out... \u00A0The disconnect was too much.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HafCoJoe","CreatedById":80363,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-09T19:37:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222711026\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145675\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470771191\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002270807\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022regex\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, regex said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNever really liked it, myself. \u00A0Seemed like a Kerbal\u0027s head would never fit inside of it\u00A0or they\u0027d be all hunched over due to ~enormous forehead~ and unable to raise their eyes up enough to actually see out... \u00A0The disconnect was too much.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nyeah... the position of Kerbal\u0027s eyes on their enormous heads would make it difficult to see out of anything that\u0027s angled like that. It suits well for side facing and steeper angled windows though. The new redesign makes a lot of sense.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-08-09T19:37:29Z\u0022 title=\u002208/09/2016 07:37  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 9, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Avera9eJoe\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SpacedCowboy","CreatedById":92106,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-09T19:39:02Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, I do kind of miss those racing stripes but like regex said, no head room.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HafCoJoe","CreatedById":80363,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-09T19:52:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222711030\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145675\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470771542\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002292106\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SpacedCowboy\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n12 minutes ago, SpacedCowboy said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, I do kind of miss those racing stripes but like regex said, no head room.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve been thinking of trying out how four black stripes would look on the front of the new cockpit... I might experiment with that later.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alshain","CreatedById":110959,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-09T20:17:18Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t think the 2nd Generation Mk1 was made by PorkJet.\u00A0 There was an intern that made a few parts just after PorkJet was brought into Squad \u003Cs\u003E(I don\u0027t remember his name)\u003C/s\u003E.\u00A0 PorkJet was still busy tweaking the Mk2 at the time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGeneration 1 - Chad Jenkins aka \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/3895-c7studios/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u00223895\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/3895-c7studios/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@C7Studios\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGeneration 2 - \u003Cspan\u003EHugo\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGeneration 3 - \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/92433-porkjet/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002292433\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/92433-porkjet/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Porkjet\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere was a Mk3 cockpit he started on too but I think it got scrapped before making it into the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-08-09T20:22:56Z\u0022 title=\u002208/09/2016 08:22  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 9, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Alshain\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HafCoJoe","CreatedById":80363,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-09T20:21:47Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222711063\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145675\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470773838\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110959\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Alshain\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n3 minutes ago, Alshain said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t think the 2nd Generation Mk1 was made by PorkJet.\u00A0 There was an intern that made a few parts just after PorkJet was brought into Squad (I don\u0027t remember his name).\u00A0 PorkJet was still busy tweaking the Mk2 at the time.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGeneration 1 - Chad Jenkins aka \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/3895-c7studios/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u00223895\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/3895-c7studios/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@C7Studios\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGeneration 2 - Intern\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nGeneration 3 - \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022 data-ipshover=\u0022\u0022 data-ipshover-target=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/92433-porkjet/\u0026amp;do=hovercard\u0022 data-mentionid=\u002292433\u0022 href=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/profile/92433-porkjet/\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003E@Porkjet\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere was a Mk3 cockpit he started on too but I think it got scrapped before making it into the game.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAh many thanks - I forgot Hugo made that model.I recall the new Mk3 cockpit he made \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u00A0it\u00A0was fun to look at for a while \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alshain","CreatedById":110959,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-09T20:22:25Z","Content":"\n\