lass=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAh many thanks - I forgot Hugo made that model.I recall the new Mk3 cockpit he made \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u00A0it\u00A0was fun to look at for a while \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAny pics of it?\u00A0 I probably missed it.\u00A0 I skipped a bunch of KSP versions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"AlamoVampire","CreatedById":78020,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-09T20:30:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nNot a big fan of regular atmospheric flight inksp but the lear jet cockpit ruins the look of fighter jet replicas. Why cant we have both?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HafCoJoe","CreatedById":80363,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-09T20:31:29Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222711074\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145675\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470774147\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u00222511\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Corona688\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n7 minutes ago, Corona688 said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI actually liked the leftmost one the best, and don\u0027t know why it needed changing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAny pics of it?\u00A0 I probably missed it.\u00A0 I skipped a bunch of KSP versions.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYe