thought it would be easier to find.\u00A0 You win!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-08-09T20:32:28Z\u0022 title=\u002208/09/2016 08:32  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 9, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Alshain\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"HafCoJoe","CreatedById":80363,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-09T20:33:32Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222711090\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145675\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470774741\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022110959\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Alshain\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, Alshain said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nLol, I was looking too.\u00A0 But I was searching in the \u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbaldevteam.tumblr.com\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Etumblr \u003C/a\u003Ecause I thought it would be easier to find.\u00A0 You win!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nxD nah\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-08-09T20:33:53Z\u0022 title=\u002208/09/2016 08:33  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 9, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Avera9eJoe\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Corona688","CreatedById":2511,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-09T20:35:24Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAh, it looks something between space shuttle and interstate bus XD\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ZooNamedGames","CreatedById":103726,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-09T21:17:59Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222711087\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145675\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470774689\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002280363\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Avera9eJoe\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n46 minutes ago, Avera9eJoe said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYep \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0The formatting in the original daily kerbal post is messed up but here it is:\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://31.media.tumblr.com/e819fdab68106cb386b463d84e158d6a/tumblr_inline_nadgl16XYm1rr2wit.jpg\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022tumblr_inline_nadgl16XYm1rr2wit.jpg\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 src=\u0022https://31.media.tumblr.com/e819fdab68106cb386b463d84e158d6a/tumblr_inline_nadgl16XYm1rr2wit.jpg\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOk it\u0027s been a LONG time since I\u0027ve played a version prior to .90, but that is \u003Cstrong\u003Enot\u003C/strong\u003E the mk3 cockpit I played with when I first started.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-08-09T21:18:12Z\u0022 title=\u002208/09/2016 09:18  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 9, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by ZooNamedGames\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ScriptKitt3h","CreatedById":82780,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-09T22:16:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI personally wish they\u0027d eventually make a single-kerbal MK2 cockpit based off the old MK1, but with the modern textures/styling of Porkjet\u0027s parts. It\u0027d be a neat way to enhance the look of single-pilot planes and SSTOs using the MK2 framework.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Wjolcz","CreatedById":39636,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-09T23:55:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe old one looked pretty bad IMO. And the new one looks good only on, well... Something that resembles a private jet.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027d rather have a cockpit that looks similar to X-1 instead (or both) except with maybe additional windows below the kerbal\u0027s feet, just so it\u0027s easier to see the ground when landing (though it wouldn\u0027t look fun reentering the atmosphere glass first).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-10T00:01:10Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t like canopies that stick out of the overall outline of the cockpit section. The distinct bump looks anti-aerodynamic. IMO the new one is much better for a civilian (space)plane as befits stock KSP, but it would be really nice to be able to paint stripes and things on our craft.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222711188\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145675\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470781010\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002282780\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022ScriptKitt3h\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 hour ago, ScriptKitt3h said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI personally wish they\u0027d eventually make a single-kerbal MK2 cockpit based off the old MK1, but with the modern textures/styling of Porkjet\u0027s parts. It\u0027d be a neat way to enhance the look of single-pilot planes and SSTOs using the MK2 framework.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe Mk2 Expansion mod has one that adapts between Mk1 at the front and Mk2 at the rear with a single pilot, if you\u0027d be interested and didn\u0027t happen to know. It is in the style of the current Mk2 though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-08-10T00:02:05Z\u0022 title=\u002208/10/2016 12:02  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00227 yr\u0022\u003EAugust 10, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Guest\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"SpacedCowboy","CreatedById":92106,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-10T02:15:46Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSometimes I wish we had a choice of the old MK-1, 2 , or 3 or the new ones. All of \u0027em in stock! ( One can only dream )\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Spuds","CreatedById":99784,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-10T02:36:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHaha, wow, it\u0027s weird seeing a (modified) comparison shot that I made over 2 years ago being dug up now! I posted the original image in \u003Ca href=\u0022https://www.reddit.com/r/KerbalSpaceProgram/comments/2c1r8y/comparing_the_new_and_old_mk1_cockpits/\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Ethis reddit thread.\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI prefer the art style of the new cockpit but like the design of the old one. IMO something like the MK1 cockpit from Ven\u0027s Stock Revamp (\u003Ca href=\u0022https://i.imgur.com/TAovKrn.jpg\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003Elink\u003C/a\u003E) would be pretty cool.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"foamyesque","CreatedById":2982,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-10T02:44:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe thing I miss most about the old Mk 1 is it\u0027s IVA. It had the most usable one out of all them, past and present. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alshain","CreatedById":110959,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-10T02:45:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222711446\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145675\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470795346\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002292106\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022SpacedCowboy\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n28 minutes ago, SpacedCowboy said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nSometimes I wish we had a choice of the old MK-1, 2 , or 3 or the new ones. All of \u0027em in stock! ( One can only dream )\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Ciframe data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/89287-105-kerbal-historical-institute-presents-original-ksp-parts-34-151115/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThere was a mod for that, it hasn\u0027t been update for the latest version unfortunately.\u00A0 I\u0027m not sure that it really needs to be updated, but it will need to be once PorkJet\u0027s rocket revamps get added in.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"ScriptKitt3h","CreatedById":82780,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-10T06:49:52Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222711323\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145675\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470787270\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022162845\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022String Witch\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 hours ago, String Witch said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI don\u0027t like canopies that stick out of the overall outline of the cockpit section. The distinct bump looks anti-aerodynamic. IMO the new one is much better for a civilian (space)plane as befits stock KSP, but it would be really nice to be able to paint stripes and things on our craft.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe Mk2 Expansion mod has one that adapts between Mk1 at the front and Mk2 at the rear with a single pilot, if you\u0027d be interested and didn\u0027t happen to know. It is in the style of the current Mk2 though.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYeah, I\u0027m hoping at some point down the line SQUAD would consider adding one similar to a mix of the 2 single-kerbal MK2 \u0022pointy\u0022 cockpits from that mod, since plenty of people would like a nice \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Single Stage to Orbit\u0022\u003ESSTO\u003C/abbr\u003E/Spaceplane-optimized MK2 single-seat cockpit that doesn\u0027t require clipping a MK1 inline into a fuselage piece (which looks decent, but can be pretty draggy sometimes and/or invite heating issues).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"W. Kerman","CreatedById":166763,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-10T07:29:27Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoy, the old mk1 cockpit was ugly. Sorry, it had to be said. It didn\u0027t fit into my ships\u0027 profiles, and I was a newbie not enjoying all of this IVA when they made the change.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut... It did look better on fighters, or at lease on crazed stock fighters I was making.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, does anyone know a way to make a Mk 3 cockpit nose cone that looks nice while not using part clipping?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Guest","CreatedById":-1,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-08-10T15:40:13Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222711619\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022145675\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221470814167\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022166763\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022W. Kerman\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n8 hours ago, W. Kerman said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoy, the old mk1 cockpit was ugly. Sorry, it had to be said. It didn\u0027t fit into my ships\u0027 profiles, and I was a newbie not enjoying all of this IVA when they made the change.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBut... It did look better on fighters, or at lease on crazed stock fighters I was making.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso, does anyone know a way to make a Mk 3 cockpit nose cone that looks nice while not using part clipping?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIMO a shielded docking port looks best there.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}